  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Support Admin",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Roles &amp; Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>General administrative duties</li>\n  <li>Prepare and send out quotations, sales orders and contracts</li>\n  <li>Handle IT product-specific sales enquiries</li>\n  <li>Assist with sourcing of new or existing products with new or current vendors</li>\n  <li>Follow-up on all sales enquiries and orders promptly with accuracy</li>\n  <li>Assist in receipt of goods delivered to office and coordinate with project coordinators in ensuring that goods are packed and labelled properly</li>\n  <li>Coordinate and Operations Team in ensuring products and/or services are out properly and delivery promptly</li>\n  <li>Inform Client and Supplier of unforeseen delays and problems</li>\n  <li>Respond to feedback from Client and facilitate after-sales support when requested</li>\n  <li>Acknowledges customers by responding to emails, texts and phone calls</li>\n  <li>Provides any necessary data or reports to the sales team</li>\n  <li>Recording sales trends and liaising with account managers to develop sales strategies</li>\n  <li>Establish active communication and engagement with all other departments to help out where necessary</li>\n  <li>Expediting requests rush orders and altering sales orders and shipping information as required</li>\n  <li>Stay up-to-date with latest sales trends and best practices</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Key Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proven work experience as a Sales administrator or Sales support agent, preferably on Cisco Tools</li>\n  <li>Hands-on experience with CRM software and MS Office (MS Excel in particular)</li>\n  <li>Understanding of sales performance metrics</li>\n  <li>Excellent organizational and multitasking skills</li>\n  <li>A team player with high level of dedication</li>\n  <li>Ability to work under strict deadlines</li>\n  <li>Certification in Marketing, Sales or relevant field is a plus</li>\n  <li>Fluent in speaking &amp; writing in English</li>\n</ul>",
